{"id":"7c41acaa6300dcbcf01d1ed845cf391a0011877754ff4f3f6e55c3d916e14c89","item_id":"c5813d9d52:0","text":"三个 MatteID AOV 设置，用于反映材质分配"}
{"id":"882c603bc7fce32a917394ce8ccbbe8a5510aaf10e5038b65089e73200974e84","item_id":"c5813d9d52:1","text":"此节点输出用于合成的 AOV。应将它连接到"}
{"id":"580d09e0548c268e55e3977560d8e47d233e14614c0855ba274fda6437adea35","item_id":"c5813d9d52:2","text":"Utility Pattern"}
{"id":"bebc23b0a02427a250242113839f122895c131654ca7edad9920dd87edc86868","item_id":"c5813d9d52:3","text":"参数，所属节点为"}
{"id":"8608905e6533fb79c29dcbee9e54642763cc7988fd456046ba16656c6564e8fd","item_id":"c5813d9d52:4","text":"PxrSurface"}
{"id":"0acf628660008381967d1312b84ffb3ea585a4d05be39c401a719e3f1a284db3","item_id":"c5813d9d52:5","text":"；它会输出 MatteID AOV。"}
{"id":"076ff90ff7c70da68feaa0136b88c874deadb7fe135d29fadaaa3fa9bfe701ae","item_id":"c5813d9d52:6","text":"它最多输出八个 RGB 遮罩（24 个遮罩），命名为"}
{"id":"25fd5755996a4101d188e50f00c23f64abd477c57a879f52807dec5adbf89a1c","item_id":"c5813d9d52:7","text":"MatteID0"}
{"id":"0660d20115b266397ba1dd9f7506ae61ff2ef2183430950cb479311799f2c58c","item_id":"c5813d9d52:8","text":"MatteID1"}
{"id":"b22d40133c42e52af8f39a5433d1e898b58f1bf88d090c0c10cd6e23ef522257","item_id":"c5813d9d52:9","text":"MatteID7"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"c5813d9d52:10","text":"。"}
{"id":"158d47362489f7548d95d8915bfeae16ea32604f618d3d8dc05b04037ee623a6","item_id":"c5813d9d52:11","text":"MatteID AOV 可用作逐对象、逐对象组、逐材质的合成遮罩。它们会正确带有运动模糊或失焦效果，让你能在合成软件中隔离对象。"}
{"id":"f43525e08ef0e19bef8b7ee99e0fad2fccd89d025c01d4f2dfaddc0d71d6c4c0","item_id":"c5813d9d52:12","text":"要将对象或着色器关联到 MatteIDx，需要向该对象或着色器添加一个特殊属性："}
{"id":"2150d9714f4da1cd3ad9ac78cafcd0513f38b7f67c54880a466a91793f964915","item_id":"c5813d9d52:13","text":"在此示例中"}
{"id":"25fd5755996a4101d188e50f00c23f64abd477c57a879f52807dec5adbf89a1c","item_id":"c5813d9d52:14","text":"MatteID0"}
{"id":"e3f423397a862a15f1a76d1c3bf59282b3b93c1f1979ad07bea73563abfe945c","item_id":"c5813d9d52:15","text":"AOV 会让你的对象显示为红色，但你可以使用绿色和蓝色通道处理另外两组对象。"}
{"id":"70e0c83c47392d835b4e494dca85b50ef63bb32b3a554c8c634d621bbcc84326","item_id":"c5813d9d52:16","text":"在 RenderMan for Maya (RfM) 中，可以通过 transform 上的 User"}
{"id":"4b0ed88f7d99420fb3ba2c68e20992280f6dcac4afaf32da17bee89c656c2ccf","item_id":"c5813d9d52:17","text":"Attributes"}
{"id":"76ce2cff7d6018e65c21fe11c683db1790627109a6d7257262c8d9a03c941b61","item_id":"c5813d9d52:18","text":"菜单添加这些属性；同时"}
{"id":"57f1bfe75ed9f1fa85046383e832473b9456d651469d441f475b657cdf1bc865","item_id":"c5813d9d52:19","text":"MatteID"}
{"id":"b34e0b5428f69f451575f80b8b209005ffbefc43eee8b7af23498274c8bbe5aa","item_id":"c5813d9d52:20","text":"选项卡位于"}
{"id":"e7ce99764a2debd20909bfcf02693d2c1aa3c6b38e1edc86fe2604296fe5e868","item_id":"c5813d9d52:21","text":"Outputs"}
{"id":"ad374486e8e536ab7beef2d93cf6019b13db95da5cd17e837f2a103aa2d77ae1","item_id":"c5813d9d52:22","text":"部分（RenderMan globals）。"}
{"id":"e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b","item_id":"c5813d9d52:23","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"id":"873163a148c76cbb91384378a3f6a141173e57cf3e343ce224624a9a12950e2a","item_id":"c5813d9d52:24","text":"Input AOV"}
{"id":"20aac582bad8cc4a7867aad0c3bfea09f71b43e3690f083a572a799f5db0778b","item_id":"c5813d9d52:25","text":"此输入只能用于串接其他不产生任何输出的节点。"}
{"id":"5342e09f2729fbc6514528e727aeb9857afb31719d43568e6b18661ace7d1014","item_id":"c5813d9d52:26","text":"Enable"}
{"id":"a6562913e3cd5d06b32c407c6deafd5052a3d30935c4634f7df5b062c1432bce","item_id":"c5813d9d52:27","text":"控制 MatteID AOV 输出。"}
{"id":"077976b8363ff3c0eeaa301318c5e92ab7865ce7989efdfe4c00140861d8b33e","item_id":"c5813d9d52:28","text":"Matte Texture(s)"}
{"id":"aa67f4d1a6e2ef56125bf74be4a16345f69b625edc59b1186bf98ea0fdeab529","item_id":"c5813d9d52:29","text":"这些参数允许为每个遮罩指定要输出的颜色或图案。该结果会乘以上述 user attribute 选择的颜色。如果将 user attribute 设为白色，此参数纹理会按原样渲染。"}
{"id":"ffa04c25b105902425b59e2e6dd0e05e36d328e87204ede56fe3932ab2cca99d","item_id":"c5813d9d52:30","text":"使用方法"}
{"id":"00a924b6e3c19428a876ce130d6004e2948aff211b4c1f83e6f2cb4511e9b44a","item_id":"c5813d9d52:31","text":"将 MatteID 节点连接到 PxrSurface 的 utilityPattern[0] 插槽。"}
{"id":"8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e","item_id":"c5813d9d52:32","text":"Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id":"e768f64d396a382d8043d4888c8b7c15e35dd3007d6f1b5907183ddff6b53670","item_id":"c5813d9d52:33","text":"resultAOV"}
{"id":"ebc35f6c08a974682a9cda2e7b0ddaa4fa446ea0e2630466a8841ce87e1c2944","item_id":"c5813d9d52:34","text":"一个整数。此输出仅用于触发图中该图案节点的执行。"}
